@startuml
title WebSocket por Salas - Componentes (Estado Atual)

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

package "Frontend" {
  component "WebSocketService" as FE_WS
  component "RoomWaitingController" as FE_WAIT
  component "GameRemoteDataSource" as FE_GAME
}

package "Backend" {
  component "WebSocket Handler\n(/ws)" as WSHandler
  component "Client" as Client
  component "Hub" as Hub
  component "RoomHub" as RoomHub

  component "CommandDispatcher" as CmdDispatcher
  component "PlayCardHandler" as PlayCardHandler
  component "ChangeBotStrategyHandler" as BotHandler

  component "EventBus" as EventBus
  component "WebSocketObserver" as WSObserver
  component "EventPersistenceObserver" as PersistObserver
}

FE_WS --> WSHandler : HTTP Upgrade
WSHandler --> Client : NewClient
WSHandler --> Hub : AddClient(roomId, client)
Hub --> RoomHub : regista cliente na sala

Client --> CmdDispatcher : mensagens {type,payload}
CmdDispatcher --> PlayCardHandler : type=play_card
CmdDispatcher --> BotHandler : type=change_bot_strategy

EventBus --> WSObserver : Update(event)
WSObserver --> Hub : BroadcastToRoom(roomId,event)
Hub --> RoomHub : Broadcast(payload)
RoomHub --> Client : Enqueue
Client --> FE_WS : frames JSON

EventBus --> PersistObserver : Update(event)

FE_WAIT ..> FE_WS : connect/watch events
FE_GAME ..> FE_WS : connect/send commands/watch events

note right of Hub
A sala precisa existir no Hub.
CreateRoom cria RoomHub explicitamente.
end note

@enduml
